T1  - Crime, community social capital and entrepreneurship: Evidence from Australian communities
AU  - Awaworyi Churchill, Sefa
AU  - Hayward, Mathew
AU  - Smyth, Russell
AU  - Trinh, Trong-Anh
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
